Betty Ross Clarke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Betty_Ross_Clarke 0 Betty Ross Clarke (born May Clarke, May 1, 1892 – January 24, 1970) was an American stage and film actress. She appeared in more than 30 films between 1920 and 1940, including silent and sound films, in both credited and uncredited roles.
